Gross Domestic Product (1991):    Pounds 210bn
Real GDP growth (1991):           7.0 per cent
Market Capitalisation:        USDollars 835.2m
Inflation rate:                   3.4 per cent
Exchange rate:            Pounds = 10.608 Yuan
 ------------------------------------------------
