FT  25 JUL 92 / UK Company News: Simon Engineering Pounds 0.5m purchase
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
Simon Engineering, the engineering, environmental and industrial services
group, has acquired the oilfield production chemical sales and services
business in the Uintah basin district of Utah from Jetco Chemicals, a
subsidiary of Procter &amp; Gamble, for Dollars 1m (Pounds 520,000).
The purchase was carried out through Simon's Unichem International
subsidiary.
